WEBVTT

01:42.560 --> 01:47.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

02:16.840 --> 02:19.680
Mr. Sun, please, have a seat.

02:19.760 --> 02:20.600
Thank you.

02:28.440 --> 02:29.480
So,

02:29.560 --> 02:34.000
Yan Zheng was the first person
you treated?

02:36.200 --> 02:37.240
Well,

02:38.080 --> 02:40.000
I couldn't just stand by
and watch him die, could I?

02:40.520 --> 02:41.600
Actually, I didn't do much.

02:41.680 --> 02:43.560
It was mostly fate.

02:46.240 --> 02:48.560
For him to meet you in such dire straits

02:48.640 --> 02:49.800
was a blessing.

02:50.320 --> 02:52.400
On behalf of Yan Zheng,
I thank you, Mr. Zhao.

02:52.920 --> 02:55.280
I don't deserve such thanks.

02:57.240 --> 02:58.120
Actually,

02:58.720 --> 03:02.040
my honorary niece carried him
back from the wilds.

03:02.120 --> 03:05.240
Otherwise, he would have frozen to death.

03:06.280 --> 03:08.080
So it seems
there was a destined connection.

03:08.160 --> 03:09.080
Of course.

03:09.160 --> 03:11.160
Otherwise, they couldn't have
gotten married, right?

03:11.960 --> 03:13.080
Marriage is good.

03:13.160 --> 03:14.080
Married?

03:14.800 --> 03:15.720
You said Jiuheng…

03:17.080 --> 03:18.120
No, no.

03:18.200 --> 03:20.840
You meant Yan Zheng took a wife?

03:20.920 --> 03:23.080
No, he married into her family.

03:23.160 --> 03:25.440
Zheng married into our family.

03:26.360 --> 03:27.640
Married into the family?

03:29.960 --> 03:32.440
Xie Jiuheng actually became
a live-in son-in-law.

03:32.960 --> 03:35.200
Who in the whole world would dare…

03:35.280 --> 03:37.320
Even the Emperor wouldn't dare
force him to marry in!

03:37.880 --> 03:39.480
At the time, he was covered in wounds.

03:39.560 --> 03:40.480
He couldn't get out of bed.

03:40.560 --> 03:45.160
Changyu slaughtered pigs to earn money
for his medicine.

03:45.680 --> 03:48.680
That saved his life too!

03:50.080 --> 03:53.200
Mrs. Fan is actually a butcher?

03:54.000 --> 03:56.040
My sister is amazing!

03:56.120 --> 03:58.640
One slap and she can knock a pig out cold!

04:00.760 --> 04:01.920
Let go of me!

04:04.720 --> 04:06.280
I'll ask you one last time.

04:06.840 --> 04:08.120
Will you marry into my family?

04:08.200 --> 04:09.240
Let go!

04:12.800 --> 04:14.080
If not,

04:14.600 --> 04:16.320
that will be your fate!

04:19.160 --> 04:20.240
I'd rather die!

04:21.120 --> 04:22.040
Let me go!

04:22.120 --> 04:24.680
Even in death,
you'll belong to this household!

04:31.080 --> 04:34.360
So Yan Zheng's choice
could be seen as rising to the occasion?

04:34.440 --> 04:36.680
No, it's repaying kindness with loyalty.

04:37.200 --> 04:39.400
But it's not entirely just repaying.

04:40.200 --> 04:42.440
This young couple,
they're very affectionate.

04:43.040 --> 04:45.720
When that ungrateful Song Yan
bullied Changyu,

04:46.240 --> 04:48.000
Yan Zheng stood up for her.

04:49.080 --> 04:50.040
And also,

04:50.120 --> 04:52.640
when her uncle tried
to seize the family property,

04:53.160 --> 04:54.960
Yan Zheng intervened.

04:55.880 --> 04:57.680
When my sister's hands crack from work,

04:57.760 --> 04:59.000
Zheng feels for her.

04:59.080 --> 05:00.840
He even buys her hand cream.

05:02.600 --> 05:04.800
Are you talking about the same person?

05:05.720 --> 05:08.760
Could Mrs. Fan have knocked
some sense out of Yan Zheng?

05:08.840 --> 05:10.160
Yes…

05:10.240 --> 05:11.800
No, no, no.

05:11.880 --> 05:13.040
His brain wasn't injured.

05:15.240 --> 05:16.760
Once he's back on his feet,

05:16.840 --> 05:18.520
he won't need to escort caravans anymore.

05:18.600 --> 05:20.000
The two of them can just

05:20.080 --> 05:22.800
run the pork stall
and live out their days in comfort.

05:24.560 --> 05:27.400
FAN'S PORK STALL

05:30.200 --> 05:31.040
Wipe my sweat!

05:42.840 --> 05:46.040
Mr. Sun, you saved Yan Zheng's life.

05:46.560 --> 05:49.520
Changyu will be back soon
to thank you properly.

05:49.600 --> 05:51.400
-She doesn't have to.
-That girl is honest and sincere.

05:51.480 --> 05:54.480
If you treat her kindly,
she'll repay you tenfold.

05:55.360 --> 05:57.160
For the great favor you've done today,

05:57.240 --> 05:59.520
Changyu will surely repay you
when she returns.

05:59.600 --> 06:00.800
Mr. Sun!

06:04.560 --> 06:05.840
Mr. Sun!

06:11.760 --> 06:13.480
So you're the one who saved my husband!

06:18.520 --> 06:20.200
This pig is for you!

06:21.040 --> 06:22.000
Yes, yes.

06:22.080 --> 06:23.080
Go on, take it.

06:23.600 --> 06:24.480
No, no…

06:24.560 --> 06:25.520
Here!

06:28.120 --> 06:29.200
Sir.

06:29.920 --> 06:31.280
Mr. Sun?

06:32.120 --> 06:33.160
Sir!

06:35.680 --> 06:37.720
Is something the matter?

06:38.520 --> 06:41.120
No, nothing, nothing.

06:41.200 --> 06:42.640
Yan Zheng!

06:44.040 --> 06:45.080
Changyu is back.

06:52.560 --> 06:53.440
Changyu, you're back!

06:54.440 --> 06:55.360
-Changyu.
-Mr. Zhao.

06:55.440 --> 06:57.200
This is the Mr. Sun
I told you about on the road.

06:57.280 --> 06:59.480
Yes, yes, this is the benefactor.

07:01.240 --> 07:02.720
No, I don't deserve it.

07:06.240 --> 07:07.800
By the way, Mr. Zhao,

07:08.320 --> 07:10.120
I have a prescription
that will restore Yan Zheng to health.

07:10.960 --> 07:12.520
That's wonderful!

07:12.600 --> 07:14.560
-I'll fetch the medicine at once!
-Quickly!

07:14.640 --> 07:16.600
Changyu, let's go get the medicine.

07:19.080 --> 07:19.960
Thank you, Mr. Sun.

07:20.680 --> 07:22.520
I should be thanking you, Mrs. Fan.

07:22.600 --> 07:24.080
Thank you for caring for him
all this time.

07:35.280 --> 07:37.040
Why hasn't he woken up yet?

07:37.120 --> 07:38.200
He's fainted?

07:39.000 --> 07:39.840
It's fine.

07:39.920 --> 07:42.040
It's the Jiuzhuan Elixir.
Fainting is to be expected.

07:42.120 --> 07:43.320
He'll wake up soon.

07:47.840 --> 07:48.880
Please, sit.

07:51.640 --> 07:52.480
Have some tea.

07:52.560 --> 07:53.400
Thank you.

08:02.600 --> 08:03.800
Are you his master?

08:05.160 --> 08:07.280
Yan Zheng serves no master.

08:08.000 --> 08:10.840
In this world, no one would dare
claim him as a subordinate.

08:14.440 --> 08:15.640
Then are you his friend?

08:18.440 --> 08:19.960
Before I arrived, I thought so.

08:20.560 --> 08:21.720
But after arriving,

08:22.240 --> 08:23.320
I found out this fellow

08:23.400 --> 08:25.800
didn't even tell me he'd gotten married.

08:25.880 --> 08:27.320
Hard to say if I'm still his friend.

08:28.080 --> 08:29.280
It happened so suddenly.

08:29.800 --> 08:31.720
You can't fault him.

08:33.840 --> 08:35.799
I was the one who begged him.

08:37.880 --> 08:39.280
You asked him to marry into your family?

08:39.360 --> 08:40.840
And he agreed to it?

08:42.640 --> 08:43.919
You could put it that way.

08:45.840 --> 08:49.400
So all those noble ladies lost
simply because they never asked?

08:50.000 --> 08:53.200
XIGU ALLEY

09:04.400 --> 09:06.000
What on earth has happened recently?

09:06.080 --> 09:08.560
How did you end up with a butcher lady?

09:10.080 --> 09:12.960
I was secretly investigating
the 16-year-old Jinzhou case.

09:13.800 --> 09:15.680
On the Chongzhou battlefield,

09:16.520 --> 09:17.760
I was struck by a hidden arrow.

09:30.600 --> 09:32.480
Xie Yi and Xie San.

09:33.400 --> 09:35.800
They fought to carve a path
through the ambush,

09:36.760 --> 09:38.560
but were cut down in the chaos.

10:47.760 --> 10:50.160
I drifted downriver to Jizhou

11:02.680 --> 11:04.320
and collapsed in the snow.

11:05.640 --> 11:07.000
She saved me.

11:08.840 --> 11:10.640
Who was after your life?

11:11.840 --> 11:13.280
I have no solid evidence yet.

11:14.320 --> 11:15.800
But I can guess it.

11:16.880 --> 11:18.240
Have you asked your uncle for help?

11:28.680 --> 11:29.960
It can't be…

11:30.480 --> 11:31.800
It's…

11:31.880 --> 11:33.440
You think Chancellor Wei wants you dead?

11:34.640 --> 11:37.720
He raised you from childhood,
sought out famous masters for you.

11:37.800 --> 11:38.640
What…

11:44.280 --> 11:46.400
What possible reason
would he have to kill you?

11:47.800 --> 11:49.000
I'd like to know myself.

11:50.880 --> 11:53.920
The moment I began
digging into the Jinzhou case,

11:55.160 --> 11:56.760
he made his move.

11:58.000 --> 11:59.640
When the Fan family was attacked,

12:00.360 --> 12:02.880
17 of Wei's Xuan Tie
death warriors were identified.

12:04.760 --> 12:08.320
The Wei clan has four ranks of death
warriors, Heaven, Earth, Xuan, and Huang.

12:08.400 --> 12:10.200
If he truly meant to kill you,

12:10.280 --> 12:12.680
a handful of Xuan guards wouldn't suffice.

12:13.280 --> 12:14.720
They were targeting Mrs. Fan?

12:15.960 --> 12:17.080
That makes less sense.

12:17.720 --> 12:19.880
The Fan family are mere commoners.

12:19.960 --> 12:21.640
They couldn't have crossed the Chancellor.

12:22.400 --> 12:23.840
Something's not right.

12:24.600 --> 12:26.080
The Fan residence was ransacked.

12:26.600 --> 12:29.320
They seemed to be searching for something.

12:31.480 --> 12:32.960
Searching for something…

12:33.480 --> 12:34.560
The Fan family…

12:35.760 --> 12:38.560
All these cases are tangled together.

12:40.320 --> 12:43.200
But you, in an instant, traced the source

12:43.280 --> 12:45.240
straight to the Fan family.

12:45.760 --> 12:46.960
As expected of you, Xie Jiuheng.

12:47.480 --> 12:49.400
I wasn't the one who found that lead.

12:51.040 --> 12:52.760
She just happened to save me.

13:19.160 --> 13:20.160
Don't turn around.

13:27.120 --> 13:28.280
Alright.

13:28.360 --> 13:30.160
Hello, Mr. Sun.

13:30.240 --> 13:31.240
Hello.

13:32.840 --> 13:35.800
You seem like such a gentle,
well-behaved child.

13:36.320 --> 13:37.320
Feeding the rabbits,

13:37.400 --> 13:38.440
tending the chickens.

13:41.360 --> 13:42.360
My falcon!

13:44.080 --> 13:46.960
Mr. Sun, you saved my sister
and brother-in-law.

13:47.480 --> 13:48.720
You're our benefactor.

13:49.320 --> 13:51.040
The falcon saved me.

13:51.120 --> 13:53.280
It's a lucky bird.

13:53.360 --> 13:55.560
Then the rabbits must grow up quickly,

13:55.640 --> 13:58.520
so the falcon can feast.

14:10.240 --> 14:11.760
Your brother-in-law saved you too?

14:11.840 --> 14:12.680
How will you repay him?

14:12.760 --> 14:15.720
When my sister
and brother-in-law have children,

14:15.800 --> 14:17.440
I'll teach them how to butcher pigs.

14:18.480 --> 14:20.600
Ning, stop playing with the rabbits.

14:20.680 --> 14:21.840
Wash the vegetables.

14:23.680 --> 14:24.800
Mr. Sun.

14:25.320 --> 14:26.160
I'll do it.

14:26.680 --> 14:28.360
How can we let a guest do chores?

14:28.440 --> 14:29.440
It's fine.

14:29.520 --> 14:31.320
I can't accept a free meal, can I?

14:32.120 --> 14:33.040
Well, thank you then.

14:33.120 --> 14:34.040
No problem.

14:36.240 --> 14:38.720
I'll make sure Yan Zheng owes me this one.

14:38.800 --> 14:40.560
Once we're back in Luyuan,

14:40.640 --> 14:42.600
I'll collect on this meal later.

14:47.560 --> 14:49.480
Yan Zheng is returning to Luyuan as well?

14:53.040 --> 14:53.920
He…

14:55.040 --> 14:56.840
He still has many unfulfilled wishes.

14:56.920 --> 14:59.040
He'll surely leave once he's recovered.

14:59.760 --> 15:00.600
He…

15:01.120 --> 15:02.600
Didn't he tell you?

15:02.680 --> 15:03.880
Once I've healed,

15:04.400 --> 15:05.640
I will be on my way.

15:06.800 --> 15:08.040
I won't trouble you further.

15:11.280 --> 15:12.320
He did.

15:13.160 --> 15:14.400
He told me.

15:16.120 --> 15:17.040
Then that's fine.

15:43.800 --> 15:46.280
You have feelings for the butcher girl?

15:49.600 --> 15:51.840
Alright, alright, I won't ask.

15:53.960 --> 15:56.200
Yesterday in court,
you forced yourself to stand tall.

15:56.720 --> 15:58.280
If I hadn't arrived in time,

15:58.360 --> 16:00.080
you might have been crippled.

16:01.200 --> 16:02.120
It was for her, right?

16:11.800 --> 16:13.280
As things stand,

16:14.160 --> 16:15.800
my country and family are still unavenged,

16:16.320 --> 16:17.920
and my wounds have not yet healed.

16:18.000 --> 16:20.960
To care for someone now
would only bring her harm.

16:21.480 --> 16:23.000
If you were me,

16:24.800 --> 16:26.400
would you allow that to happen?

16:31.440 --> 16:32.440
People

16:33.840 --> 16:36.440
are not immortals without feeling.

16:37.560 --> 16:38.880
Matters of the heart

16:40.880 --> 16:42.200
are hard to control.

16:48.320 --> 16:49.520
You should return early.

16:50.040 --> 16:51.640
Keep a close eye on Wei Yan for me.

16:52.280 --> 16:54.160
Now the battlefield is changing rapidly.

16:55.200 --> 16:57.880
That incompetent Wei Xuan
now commands the armies.

16:58.760 --> 17:00.680
The northwest is bound for upheaval.

17:01.280 --> 17:03.000
I cannot conceal my identity

17:03.560 --> 17:04.400
much longer.

17:04.920 --> 17:06.880
Prince Changxin
will certainly march south.

17:07.400 --> 17:08.599
General He

17:09.240 --> 17:10.839
will struggle to hold the line.

17:10.920 --> 17:13.920
Then, Marquis, why not
depart with me tomorrow?

17:38.320 --> 17:39.160
Changyu.

17:39.240 --> 17:41.600
Your family's case has been closed
by the magistrate.

17:41.680 --> 17:43.120
QINGPING COUNTY YAMEN

17:43.840 --> 17:44.680
Mr. Wang.

17:44.760 --> 17:46.160
The mastermind is still at large.

17:46.240 --> 17:47.560
How can the case be closed?

17:48.920 --> 17:51.320
Those killed in the pine forest
were deemed the culprits.

17:51.880 --> 17:53.480
Bandits from Qingfeng Stronghold.

17:54.560 --> 17:56.080
They were bandits?

17:57.360 --> 17:59.320
Why would bandits ransack my home?

17:59.840 --> 18:00.800
I'm thinking,

18:00.880 --> 18:03.520
perhaps your father offended someone

18:04.040 --> 18:05.440
during his escort days.

18:06.800 --> 18:07.960
Changyu, listen to me.

18:08.640 --> 18:11.080
Sell off the family's pig pens,
house, and land.

18:11.600 --> 18:13.680
Go elsewhere
and keep a low profile for now.

18:16.040 --> 18:17.040
Father, Mother,

18:18.920 --> 18:20.280
tell me.

18:20.360 --> 18:22.040
Should I take Ning and leave?

18:24.120 --> 18:25.200
Tell me.

18:25.280 --> 18:27.280
Would Yan Zheng go with us?

18:31.120 --> 18:32.600
I fear I've dragged him into this.

18:39.440 --> 18:40.840
Changyu.

18:40.920 --> 18:42.520
Why are you sitting here alone?

18:43.160 --> 18:44.000
What's wrong, Mrs. Wang?

18:44.080 --> 18:46.280
Do you have rich relatives visiting?

18:46.360 --> 18:47.960
-Why?
-The carriage from your house

18:48.040 --> 18:51.360
was even finer
than the Song family's when they moved!

18:56.880 --> 18:58.360
Don't forget your basket!

19:22.680 --> 19:24.800
‎MARRIAGE

19:47.120 --> 19:48.720
HAVE A FULL MEAL

19:52.400 --> 19:53.400
"Today,

19:53.480 --> 19:54.720
I

19:55.400 --> 19:56.800
take my leave of Mrs. Fan.

19:57.840 --> 19:59.320
May you live in peace."

20:16.280 --> 20:17.400
Changyu.

20:18.760 --> 20:19.800
Has Zheng left?

20:24.880 --> 20:26.000
It's good that he's left.

20:27.160 --> 20:28.280
It's good that he's left.

20:29.120 --> 20:31.000
If trouble comes again,

20:31.080 --> 20:32.600
he won't be dragged into it.

20:35.880 --> 20:37.600
Why didn't you say goodbye?

20:42.440 --> 20:44.120
Zheng is back!

21:00.520 --> 21:01.920
Yan Zheng, you…

21:06.840 --> 21:10.200
Zheng went to Madam Zhuang's
to read a letter for her mother-in-law.

21:12.080 --> 21:13.320
The old lady can't walk.

21:13.400 --> 21:14.600
I went to read it for her.

21:19.160 --> 21:21.400
What's wrong? Were you crying?

21:24.080 --> 21:25.040
I wasn't!

21:25.960 --> 21:27.760
The smoke from curing the meat
stung my eyes.

21:31.560 --> 21:32.800
Sun has left.

21:32.880 --> 21:34.360
He left some money.

21:38.280 --> 21:40.840
Mr. Sun likes things neat and tidy.

21:40.920 --> 21:44.440
He even cleaned the whole house
before he left.

21:51.520 --> 21:53.760
I came to look for straw rope

21:53.840 --> 21:55.160
to hang the bacon.

22:18.080 --> 22:19.320
Why did I grab an iron chain?

22:23.760 --> 22:26.920
To cure bacon, you salt it
for seven or eight days,

22:27.000 --> 22:28.640
then smoke it with cypress branches.

22:28.720 --> 22:30.720
That way, it keeps longer.

22:30.800 --> 22:31.840
Look.

22:32.360 --> 22:33.960
The meat I cured a few days ago

22:34.040 --> 22:35.440
is almost ready.

22:35.520 --> 22:36.920
Tomorrow I'll take some to Grandpa.

22:37.720 --> 22:38.920
The medicine's on the table.
Drink while it's warm.

22:40.920 --> 22:41.760
All right.

22:44.880 --> 22:46.120
I went to the Yamen today.

22:46.760 --> 22:48.920
Mr. Wang said the case was closed.

22:49.880 --> 22:51.080
But we still don't know

22:51.160 --> 22:53.400
whether they came to rob us

22:53.480 --> 22:55.320
or for revenge.

22:58.080 --> 22:59.720
If they came for revenge,

23:00.240 --> 23:01.800
they will definitely come back.

23:03.360 --> 23:04.480
What's your plan?

23:05.920 --> 23:08.720
I plan to sell the family property
after the Spring Festival.

23:09.480 --> 23:11.960
Then take Ning and lie low
somewhere else for a while.

23:14.280 --> 23:16.680
If we're going, the sooner the better.

23:17.760 --> 23:19.400
But the Spring Festival
is around the corner,

23:19.480 --> 23:20.960
and it's snowing outside.

23:21.720 --> 23:23.320
The transfer papers
for selling the property

23:23.400 --> 23:24.960
will take some time to process.

23:25.480 --> 23:26.680
By then,

23:26.760 --> 23:28.760
your wounds will have healed.

23:28.840 --> 23:30.040
What do you think?

23:32.520 --> 23:33.360
Me?

23:34.960 --> 23:36.720
The Zhao couple are kind people.

23:37.320 --> 23:40.240
Their son died in battle.

23:40.320 --> 23:42.240
I want to leave them the fields to farm.

23:43.040 --> 23:45.480
I'll draw up the divorce letter for you

23:46.280 --> 23:48.440
and leave you money for the road.

23:51.000 --> 23:52.280
I have my own plans.

23:53.200 --> 23:54.320
Don't worry about me.

23:55.960 --> 23:57.240
Do you want to come with me?

24:02.320 --> 24:05.160
Or do you want to stay here to recuperate?

24:08.560 --> 24:09.720
I'll go with you.

24:14.400 --> 24:16.280
Then help me hang this bacon.

24:36.160 --> 24:37.360
Are there any keepsakes

24:37.440 --> 24:39.600
from your parents
you want to take with you?

24:43.240 --> 24:44.080
Yes.

24:47.000 --> 24:47.840
The knives.

24:48.480 --> 24:50.560
I'll take that set with me wherever I go.

24:50.640 --> 24:53.000
With them, I can make
a living slaughtering pigs.

24:53.520 --> 24:56.320
If we run into trouble on the road,
we can defend ourselves.

24:57.200 --> 24:58.080
Anything else?

24:59.640 --> 25:00.480
The title deed.

25:01.440 --> 25:03.240
Since the case is closed,

25:03.320 --> 25:04.920
I'll take it out.

25:05.520 --> 25:06.840
The title deed…

25:07.720 --> 25:09.880
Did your parents ever tell you

25:09.960 --> 25:11.320
what to take

25:11.400 --> 25:13.480
if you had to flee for your life?

25:16.840 --> 25:18.160
-Yes.
-What is it?

25:18.800 --> 25:19.680
My sister.

25:28.680 --> 25:29.600
Your sister.

25:34.240 --> 25:35.680
Candied tangerine peel. I tried some.

25:35.760 --> 25:38.280
Sweet and sour. It cuts the bitterness.

25:39.800 --> 25:40.840
Thank you.

25:43.560 --> 25:45.680
Such a shame.

25:45.760 --> 25:49.080
Her days will only grow harder from here.

25:50.520 --> 25:52.600
That girl brings misfortune.

25:53.920 --> 25:55.840
She brought ruin to her parents,

25:55.920 --> 25:57.560
and even her uncle wasn't spared.

25:58.160 --> 26:00.160
Fan Daniu was perfectly fine.

26:00.240 --> 26:02.720
How did he end up killed by bandits?

26:02.800 --> 26:04.160
Who knows?

26:04.240 --> 26:07.000
Maybe Fan Changyu paid to have him killed!

26:07.080 --> 26:08.640
Kang, you shut your mouth!

26:09.160 --> 26:11.160
Think of your two grandsons
and mind your virtue!

26:11.240 --> 26:13.560
Your eldest son is dead,

26:13.640 --> 26:15.040
and your daughter-in-law ran off.

26:15.120 --> 26:17.040
That's your ill fate
bringing ruin on them.

26:17.120 --> 26:18.680
That's nonsense!

26:21.240 --> 26:22.280
Changyu.

26:23.240 --> 26:24.320
Changyu is here!

26:25.040 --> 26:26.360
Why is she here?

26:26.960 --> 26:28.680
Fan Changyu!

26:29.640 --> 26:31.000
Fan Changyu!

26:31.600 --> 26:33.040
You dare show your face here?

26:34.640 --> 26:37.400
-Grab her.
-Damn you. I'll beat you to death!

26:41.080 --> 26:42.600
-Ah…
-Are you all right?

26:42.680 --> 26:43.520
-Changyu!
-You…

26:43.600 --> 26:45.400
-How could you?
-Shameless!

26:46.080 --> 26:48.000
-Changyu!
-You bringer of misfortune!

26:48.080 --> 26:50.120
-I'm fine.
-Wasn't Fan Daniu's death enough for you?

26:50.200 --> 26:51.720
You dare come to my house?

26:51.800 --> 26:53.280
I'll teach you a lesson!

26:55.440 --> 26:56.360
I came

26:56.440 --> 26:58.320
to bring something for Grandpa,

26:59.080 --> 27:00.480
not to cause trouble.

27:01.080 --> 27:02.560
Step past this knife

27:03.160 --> 27:04.600
and I'll cut out your foul tongue.

27:07.040 --> 27:07.880
What's going on?

27:07.960 --> 27:09.200
What's happening here?

27:10.160 --> 27:11.080
Grandpa.

27:12.040 --> 27:13.400
I brought you some cured bacon.

27:13.480 --> 27:15.000
You're here, Changyu.

27:19.000 --> 27:20.200
How is your health?

27:21.640 --> 27:22.640
Has anyone been giving you trouble?

27:22.720 --> 27:23.840
No.

27:24.360 --> 27:25.960
No one dares.

27:26.880 --> 27:27.960
Changyu.

27:28.800 --> 27:31.760
Daniu and Erniu are both gone now.

27:33.200 --> 27:34.440
There's something

27:35.040 --> 27:36.840
I must tell you.

27:38.000 --> 27:41.400
-Actually, your father, he was my…
-Ever since her father,

27:41.480 --> 27:42.600
Fan Erniu,

27:43.160 --> 27:44.120
returned,

27:44.200 --> 27:46.320
our days have been nothing but misery!

27:46.400 --> 27:50.080
My Daniu was cursed to death
by her family!

27:51.400 --> 27:54.880
Sooner or later,
she'll bring ruin on us all!

27:57.800 --> 28:00.000
Grandpa, take care of your health.

28:00.080 --> 28:02.160
I'll leave now.
I'll come see you another day.

28:16.520 --> 28:17.920
-Look! Look!
-This is unacceptable.

28:18.000 --> 28:18.960
-This ungrateful girl.
-Go away!

28:19.040 --> 28:21.760
She won't even pay respects to her uncle!

28:21.840 --> 28:23.280
Calm down.

28:24.680 --> 28:27.000
What a retribution.

28:32.760 --> 28:35.440
SOUTH MARKET

28:35.520 --> 28:37.440
FAN'S PORK STALL

28:38.480 --> 28:39.400
Come take a look!

28:39.480 --> 28:40.320
Here you go.

28:40.400 --> 28:41.400
Come take a look!

28:41.480 --> 28:42.880
PORK

28:42.960 --> 28:43.840
Changyu.

28:45.640 --> 28:46.600
Closing up so early?

28:47.800 --> 28:49.600
Mr. Li, I'm not doing business today.

28:49.680 --> 28:51.120
You won't even sell to me?

28:53.040 --> 28:54.680
Something happened at home.

28:55.720 --> 28:58.440
I won't reopen until after the New Year.

28:58.520 --> 29:00.760
I'm not here to buy meat today.

29:00.840 --> 29:02.120
My landlord wants to meet you.

29:04.640 --> 29:05.920
-Madam…
-Welcome,

29:06.000 --> 29:06.960
please, come in.

29:07.040 --> 29:08.000
YIXIANG RESTAURANT

29:09.480 --> 29:10.600
-You're back, sir.
-Yes.

29:11.480 --> 29:12.680
This way.

29:12.760 --> 29:13.800
Take care.

29:13.880 --> 29:15.240
Changyu, look.

29:15.760 --> 29:17.840
This is the main hall
of our Yixiang Restaurant.

29:18.440 --> 29:20.360
-Look around.
-Magnificent!

29:20.880 --> 29:21.960
Of course!

29:22.480 --> 29:24.600
This is the finest restaurant
in all of Lin'an!

29:25.600 --> 29:27.120
It's not even packed right now.

29:27.200 --> 29:28.480
During the Spring Festival,

29:28.560 --> 29:30.360
it'll be so crowded,
you won't find room to stand.

29:30.440 --> 29:31.320
So bustling!

29:33.800 --> 29:34.640
You're back, Chef.

29:36.920 --> 29:38.240
It's enormous!

29:38.320 --> 29:39.560
Come, Changyu. This way.

29:42.000 --> 29:43.240
I'll leave you here.

29:43.320 --> 29:44.320
The owner is inside.

29:44.400 --> 29:45.360
You may go in.

30:25.840 --> 30:28.000
Ms. Yu, Mrs. Fan is here.

30:31.680 --> 30:33.400
Changyu is here?

30:48.720 --> 30:52.080
So you're the owner of Yixiang Restaurant?

30:52.160 --> 30:53.840
I always thought

30:54.360 --> 30:56.360
the owner here was a man.

30:58.040 --> 30:59.600
Before I met you,

30:59.680 --> 31:01.640
I never imagined a butcher lady

31:01.720 --> 31:03.000
could be so beautiful!

31:04.320 --> 31:06.400
You're the real beauty here.

31:08.320 --> 31:10.080
My name is Yu Qianqian.

31:10.160 --> 31:11.680
I'm a few years your senior.

31:12.320 --> 31:14.880
If you don't mind, I'll call you Changyu.

31:15.480 --> 31:16.760
Chef Li Deqin says

31:16.840 --> 31:18.560
you butcher well,

31:18.640 --> 31:20.160
and your braised pork is exceptional.

31:21.320 --> 31:23.160
Thank you for the praise.

31:23.240 --> 31:25.040
Don't be modest.

31:25.560 --> 31:26.920
I saw

31:27.000 --> 31:28.880
you smashed the Wang family's signboard.

31:32.200 --> 31:33.920
That's true.

31:34.440 --> 31:35.720
But I didn't strike first.

31:36.320 --> 31:37.960
No matter who struck first,

31:38.040 --> 31:39.720
you were definitely not wrong.

31:39.800 --> 31:43.400
Since the Wang heir took over,

31:43.480 --> 31:46.240
he's been dishonest.
And he's light-fingered as well.

31:46.320 --> 31:48.000
I've long wanted to cut ties with them.

31:50.920 --> 31:52.080
Bring it up.

31:54.840 --> 31:55.760
Bring it in.

32:00.840 --> 32:01.680
To be frank,

32:01.760 --> 32:04.960
I had someone buy your braised pork
for ten days straight.

32:05.040 --> 32:06.680
The quality and portions never changed.

32:07.280 --> 32:08.280
Very honest of you.

32:09.640 --> 32:11.440
This is how business should be done.

32:11.520 --> 32:12.560
My father used to say

32:12.640 --> 32:14.080
a business built on guilt won't last.

32:14.960 --> 32:18.440
So, I'd like to do
this braised pork business

32:19.720 --> 32:20.960
with you.

32:23.560 --> 32:25.280
Thank you for your appreciation.

32:25.920 --> 32:28.400
But I'm afraid I can't.

32:29.040 --> 32:31.720
-Why?
-Something happened at my home.

32:32.240 --> 32:34.080
After the festival,
I'll be leaving Lin'an.

32:37.920 --> 32:39.440
In that case,

32:39.520 --> 32:41.880
Lin'an will lose a fine delicacy.

32:45.560 --> 32:47.240
If you really like it, I can give you

32:47.800 --> 32:49.400
the ingredients and the recipe.

32:51.200 --> 32:53.600
You can have your cooks
prepare it accordingly.

32:59.840 --> 33:01.520
You're truly straightforward.

33:01.600 --> 33:04.160
We only chatted a little,
and you've already laid everything bare.

33:05.600 --> 33:08.440
If you go elsewhere, stay sharp.

33:09.840 --> 33:12.440
Mr. Li and my father
were friends for many years.

33:13.080 --> 33:14.720
When my father was alive,

33:14.800 --> 33:16.760
he often brought business
to our pork stall.

33:16.840 --> 33:18.280
I thought,

33:18.920 --> 33:20.600
since Mr. Li is such a good man,

33:21.120 --> 33:23.680
his landlord must be as well.

33:26.560 --> 33:27.960
If I give you the recipe,

33:28.480 --> 33:30.280
the people of Lin'an

33:30.360 --> 33:32.040
can still taste my parents' cooking.

33:32.560 --> 33:35.080
Their spirits would surely approve.

33:44.760 --> 33:45.640
Come with me.

33:51.640 --> 33:52.480
Look.

33:53.000 --> 33:55.360
During the Spring Festival,
business is at its peak.

33:55.440 --> 33:57.280
All banquet tables are fully booked.

33:57.360 --> 33:59.480
Demand for braised pork
is naturally high as well.

34:00.240 --> 34:02.360
Those diners have very discerning tastes.

34:02.440 --> 34:03.840
How about this?

34:03.920 --> 34:06.480
You supply braised pork
through the festival.

34:07.000 --> 34:10.040
After the festival,
I'll find another solution.

34:11.800 --> 34:13.639
Relocating and buying a new home

34:13.719 --> 34:15.199
will cost you a great deal.

34:15.800 --> 34:16.960
I'll pay you extra.

34:17.040 --> 34:19.840
Help me get through
the Spring Festival rush first.

34:21.920 --> 34:24.120
It's good money for you too.

34:25.880 --> 34:27.199
Then thank you, Ms. Yu.

34:28.320 --> 34:29.679
I should be thanking you.

34:30.600 --> 34:31.920
With the Wang's,

34:32.000 --> 34:34.840
I paid 40 wen per jin year-round,
busy season or slow.

34:34.920 --> 34:36.239
Meat prices have risen.

34:36.320 --> 34:37.719
Your product is good.

34:38.239 --> 34:40.280
I'll pay you 50 wen per jin.

34:41.120 --> 34:43.440
You can braise the pork in our kitchen.
Payment will be made daily.

34:44.800 --> 34:45.760
This is too much.

34:45.840 --> 34:46.880
No.

34:47.400 --> 34:49.520
Be generous in favors,
but clear in business.

34:50.400 --> 34:51.280
Let's say…

34:51.360 --> 34:53.360
Come tomorrow.
I'll have a contract drawn up.

34:54.239 --> 34:56.719
To show my sincerity,
I'll pay a deposit upfront.

34:57.320 --> 34:58.360
Fuling.

35:01.280 --> 35:02.440
This… This won't do.

35:02.520 --> 35:05.280
The contract isn't signed yet.
I can't accept this.

35:05.360 --> 35:06.400
It wouldn't be proper.

35:07.120 --> 35:09.120
I'm worried you might change your mind!

35:09.760 --> 35:11.080
Just take it.

35:11.840 --> 35:14.160
If you refuse, I won't be at ease.

35:20.600 --> 35:21.960
Then I'll accept it.

35:22.480 --> 35:23.320
Thank you, Ms. Yu.

35:24.760 --> 35:26.960
I'm in good spirits today.
Why call me Miss?

35:28.000 --> 35:29.000
Just call me…

35:29.840 --> 35:30.680
Qian.

35:33.520 --> 35:34.680
Thank you, Qian.

35:42.240 --> 35:45.640
Where's the owner? Come out!

35:45.720 --> 35:47.560
You there, stop playing the pipa!

35:48.080 --> 35:50.520
Li Deqin, get out here!

35:50.600 --> 35:52.520
Guo Dali, what are you doing here?

35:52.600 --> 35:53.440
Why cut ties with me?

35:53.520 --> 35:56.240
We only cooperated
because the Fan family was in trouble.

35:56.320 --> 35:57.960
Now the agreed date has come.

35:58.040 --> 35:59.080
Don't you know that?

35:59.160 --> 36:00.920
Nonsense!

36:02.200 --> 36:03.880
When you were short on supply,
you came to me.

36:03.960 --> 36:05.480
Now that Fan Changyu is back,

36:05.560 --> 36:07.520
you're kicking me out?

36:07.600 --> 36:09.120
I'm telling you, no way!

36:09.200 --> 36:10.880
Today, you're taking this meat,

36:10.960 --> 36:12.520
whether you like it or not.

36:13.680 --> 36:15.680
Qian, this butcher Guo Dali

36:15.760 --> 36:18.240
sells water-injected meat
with borax mixed in.

36:18.320 --> 36:19.840
It looks fresh, but tastes foul.

36:19.920 --> 36:21.920
-Don't shout!
-He's notorious for it in our trade.

36:22.000 --> 36:23.040
Get away! Get away!

36:23.120 --> 36:26.480
-Ms. Yu will not see you!
-Not coming out? I'll tell some secrets!

36:27.760 --> 36:30.080
This cook Li Deqin.

36:30.160 --> 36:34.360
He's carrying on with that Fan Changyu!

36:34.440 --> 36:35.960
-This…
-Are you crazy?

36:36.040 --> 36:37.800
He's still spewing slander!

36:37.880 --> 36:39.040
My father warned him about this long ago.

36:39.120 --> 36:40.600
Look at you. At your age…

36:40.680 --> 36:42.080
-I'll deal with him!
-You shameless dog.

36:42.160 --> 36:43.680
-Changyu!
-What should I call you?

36:43.760 --> 36:45.520
-Calm down
-Ever vigorous?

36:45.600 --> 36:48.040
-Still sharp in your old age?
-This is my restaurant.

36:48.120 --> 36:50.040
-Just watch.
-You've no shame!

36:51.000 --> 36:52.080
-Hmph!
-Get down here!

36:52.160 --> 36:53.840
-Ms. Yu!
-I'll kill you!

36:53.920 --> 36:55.080
If you still don't come out,

36:55.160 --> 36:57.840
I'll spill more secrets!

36:57.920 --> 36:59.160
-What's going on?
-Come down!

37:01.520 --> 37:04.240
-Ms. Yu!
-It's you, Guo Dali.

37:04.320 --> 37:06.320
I run an open-door business.

37:06.400 --> 37:08.520
With you causing a scene,
how am I to do business?

37:09.960 --> 37:12.120
Ms. Yu, finally, you come out.

37:14.720 --> 37:16.680
Of all the damn places to run into you.

37:18.360 --> 37:19.880
Ms. Yu.

37:19.960 --> 37:22.160
Your people

37:22.240 --> 37:25.160
are up to sneaking, stealing,

37:25.240 --> 37:28.040
and shameless affairs all day long!
Are you in charge here

37:28.120 --> 37:29.840
-or not?
-Shut up!

37:30.760 --> 37:32.920
You speak with remarkable detail.

37:33.000 --> 37:35.680
Did you crawl under the bed
and witness it yourself?

37:35.760 --> 37:36.840
You saw it?

37:39.080 --> 37:41.280
I advise you, Ms. Yu,

37:41.360 --> 37:43.240
you'd better give me an explanation today.

37:43.320 --> 37:46.120
You know Clerk Guo?

37:46.960 --> 37:49.440
He's my father's cousin, mind you.

37:50.240 --> 37:53.600
If I report this matter to him,

37:53.680 --> 37:54.560
Ms. Yu,

37:54.640 --> 37:58.360
you won't be able
to bear the consequences.

37:58.880 --> 38:00.560
What a coincidence.

38:00.640 --> 38:03.720
He is drinking tea in the private room
in the back hall right now.

38:03.800 --> 38:05.480
Shall we ask him to judge?

38:05.560 --> 38:06.760
That's right!

38:08.720 --> 38:09.720
Is that so?

38:10.240 --> 38:12.400
Alright then, let's go.

38:16.080 --> 38:17.640
-Take the meat inside.
-Get lost!

38:20.320 --> 38:22.080
Men, throw that meat out!

38:23.400 --> 38:25.000
It's alright. It's alright.

38:25.080 --> 38:26.400
Continue the music!

38:26.480 --> 38:28.560
There will be song and dance shortly.

38:29.080 --> 38:30.000
Everyone, relax.

38:30.080 --> 38:31.280
Eat well and drink well.

38:37.880 --> 38:38.880
This way.

38:43.960 --> 38:44.800
Please.

38:48.840 --> 38:50.880
Clerk Guo? Are you inside?

38:51.560 --> 38:52.400
Father is inside!

38:54.080 --> 38:56.480
In my territory, a nobody
like you doesn't run wild!

38:56.560 --> 38:58.400
See if I don't teach you a lesson today!

38:58.480 --> 38:59.440
Ms. Yu!

38:59.520 --> 39:00.720
This mink coat is expensive!

39:00.800 --> 39:02.520
Perhaps that's enough?

39:02.600 --> 39:04.400
Right, I almost forgot.

39:09.280 --> 39:11.280
Changyu, were you scared?

39:12.920 --> 39:14.880
Teach him a lesson, but don't go too far.

39:14.960 --> 39:16.120
Understood!

39:16.200 --> 39:17.920
Come on. Nothing good to see here.

39:18.000 --> 39:19.360
Not as fun as butchering pigs.

39:22.440 --> 39:23.560
Hit him!

39:25.080 --> 39:27.280
-Not the face!
-Let me tell you.

39:27.360 --> 39:29.240
We have a show up front. It's really good.

39:29.320 --> 39:30.840
Come. Let's go watch.

40:01.360 --> 40:02.240
Bravo!

40:02.320 --> 40:03.360
Bravo!

40:10.960 --> 40:11.800
Sir, look.

40:12.320 --> 40:13.520
The young lady from that day.

40:15.120 --> 40:16.840
The one who lost her shoe.

40:16.920 --> 40:18.200
Her name is Fan Changyu.

40:18.280 --> 40:20.400
So we'd already met without realizing it.

40:21.520 --> 40:22.880
Fan Changyu…

40:25.960 --> 40:27.680
Have our people in Lin'an
watch her closely.

40:27.760 --> 40:28.680
The death warriors as well.

40:29.280 --> 40:30.760
For now, don't alert the magistrate.

40:30.840 --> 40:32.480
I'll speak to the coroner in person.

40:33.000 --> 40:33.840
Yes.

40:44.480 --> 40:45.520
Changyu, you're back?

40:45.600 --> 40:46.440
I'm back.

40:49.040 --> 40:49.880
Changyu.

40:53.360 --> 40:54.360
I'm back!

40:55.640 --> 40:56.520
Changyu!

40:57.040 --> 40:57.880
Come!

41:00.280 --> 41:01.320
Look!

41:02.000 --> 41:04.120
All these are for me?

41:04.200 --> 41:06.000
For you and Zheng.

41:06.080 --> 41:07.360
He doesn't like bitter things.

41:07.440 --> 41:08.920
Neither do you.

41:09.840 --> 41:11.360
-You're back?
-Mrs. Zhao!

41:11.440 --> 41:13.160
You bought so much. What's this?

41:14.080 --> 41:16.120
So much candy!
Is it Spring Festival already?

41:16.720 --> 41:18.320
I went to Yixiang Restaurant
to discuss business.

41:18.400 --> 41:19.320
They're from Yu Qianqian.

41:20.080 --> 41:21.440
That restaurant owner Ms. Yu?

41:22.320 --> 41:24.680
I didn't expect her to be quite nice.

41:25.720 --> 41:28.880
For a woman to run two restaurants,
here and in the county town,

41:28.960 --> 41:29.800
is truly impressive.

41:29.880 --> 41:31.360
You know about her too?

41:31.440 --> 41:32.280
Of course.

41:33.080 --> 41:35.400
Back then, she came to Lin'an pregnant

41:36.040 --> 41:37.040
and alone.

41:37.120 --> 41:39.680
-Circumstances were worse than yours.
-Where is her husband?

41:40.680 --> 41:41.760
I'm not sure.

41:41.840 --> 41:43.120
He must have been wealthy.

41:43.200 --> 41:45.640
Otherwise, how could he have married
such a capable wife?

42:05.040 --> 42:06.440
Ning's staying here tonight.

42:06.520 --> 42:08.160
Aren't you heading back?

42:10.400 --> 42:11.640
I'll roast the persimmons.

42:12.760 --> 42:14.040
That tree won't topple.

42:14.120 --> 42:16.120
You can roast persimmons your whole life.

42:17.400 --> 42:19.480
Can you stay married your whole life
without consummating?

42:26.200 --> 42:28.240
Auntie, actually, Yan Zheng and I…

42:29.720 --> 42:31.920
Didn't you say Yan Zheng
agreed to leave with you?

42:32.680 --> 42:35.520
He said he'd leave with me for now.

42:36.040 --> 42:37.000
What about after that?

42:37.080 --> 42:38.880
Why worry about what comes after?

42:39.480 --> 42:41.600
In a matrilocal marriage,
you should take the initiative.

42:42.240 --> 42:44.080
I don't care what you're thinking.

42:44.600 --> 42:47.600
I can see Yan Zheng is a fine man.

42:47.680 --> 42:50.080
Look at what happened
to your family this time.

42:50.160 --> 42:53.000
He went to save Changning
despite his injuries.

42:53.080 --> 42:54.200
And also,

42:54.280 --> 42:55.200
in the yamen court,

42:55.280 --> 42:57.120
If Mr. Sun hadn't arrived in time,

42:57.200 --> 42:59.800
he would've fought the magistrate
to the bitter end.

43:02.760 --> 43:04.280
A man with a sense of responsibility.

43:04.360 --> 43:08.240
Why not seize the chance
to consummate the marriage?

43:08.320 --> 43:09.520
Once you've shared a bed,

43:09.600 --> 43:11.240
his heart will stay with you.

43:11.320 --> 43:12.400
But…

43:12.920 --> 43:16.440
If I force it for no reason,
what would that make me?

43:16.520 --> 43:19.040
What's wrong with being close
to your own husband?

43:19.120 --> 43:21.120
Do you need an auspicious day for it?

43:21.200 --> 43:22.880
Mrs. Zhao!

43:23.960 --> 43:25.200
All right, all right.

43:25.720 --> 43:26.960
I'll give you another trick.

43:28.680 --> 43:31.080
That bedding you spread
on the floor in your bridal room,

43:31.600 --> 43:33.120
I washed it for you today.

43:35.080 --> 43:37.240
You think he'll let you
sleep bare like that?

44:08.560 --> 44:09.800
Come here.

46:48.560 --> 46:52.280
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:52.360 --> 46:53.240
Subtitle translation by: Peng Peng
